name: Animations
tagline: A component collection of CSS3 animations taken from the animate.css library
body:
## Collections [esundahl/attention-seekers](https://github.com/esundahl/attention-seekers) - Attention seeking animations [esundahl/bouncing-entrances](https://github.com/esundahl/bouncing-entrances) - Bouncing entrance animations [esundahl/bouncing-exits](https://github.com/esundahl/bouncing-exits) - Bouncing exit animations [esundahl/fading-entrances](https://github.com/esundahl/fading-entrances) - Fading entrance animations [esundahl/fading-exits](https://github.com/esundahl/fading-exits) - Fading exit animations [esundahl/flippers](https://github.com/esundahl/flippers) - Flipper Animations [esundahl/light-speed](https://github.com/esundahl/light-speed) - Light speed animations [esundahl/rotating-entrances](https://github.com/esundahl/rotating-entrances) - Rotating entrance animations [esundahl/rotating-exits](https://github.com/esundahl/rotating-exits) - Rotating exit animations [esundahl/specials](https://github.com/esundahl/specials) - Special animations ## Individual Animations
